<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM8.7">
<l>āliṉilaip pālakaṉā yaṉṟulaka muṇṭavaṉē</l>
<l>vāliyaikkoṉ ṟaraciḷaiya vāṉarattuk kaḷittavaṉē</l>
<l>kāliṉmaṇi karaiyalaikkuṅ kaṇapuratteṉ karumaṇiyē</l>
<l>ālinakark katipatiyē yayōttimaṉē tālēlō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who swallowed the world that day as an infant on a banyan leaf!</l>
<l>O You who, having killed Vālin, gave [his] kingdom to the young monkey!</l>
<l>O Apple of my eye from Kaṇapuram, where due to the wind, pearls dash against the shores!</l>
<l>O king of the town of Āli! O King of Ayodhyā, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
